Privacy Policy
BLUEHEART TECHNOLOGIES LTD is a UK Limited company that develops and publishes the Blueheart Therapy app. This privacy policy will explain how our organization uses the personal data we collect from you when you use our app or website.
Topics:
What data do we collect?
How do we collect your data?
How will we use your data?
How do we store your data?
Marketing
What are your data protection rights?
What are cookies?
How do we use cookies?
